OL,6,FA 39-year-old woman has appeared in
OL,7,Fcourt charged with causing the death
OL,8,Fof a nine-year-old boy by dangerous
OL,9,Fdriving.
OL,11,FZac Roe, from Andover in Hampshire,
OL,12,Fwho died at the scene of the crash in
OL,13,FEast Woodyates, north Dorset, on 25
OL,14,FMarch 2024, was described by his
OL,15,Ffamily as their "best buddy" and
OL,16,F"little angel".
