OL,6,FDorset Police were called to a report
OL,7,Fof the accident on the A354 Salisbury
OL,8,FRoad involving a cattle transporter
OL,9,Ftruck and trailer, a white Ford
OL,10,FTransit van and a grey Citroen car.
OL,12,FBarbara Roe, of Andover Road,
OL,13,FLudgershall, Wiltshire, appeared at
OL,14,FPoole Magistrates' Court, where she
OL,15,Fdid not enter a plea to the single
OL,16,Fcharge.
OL,18,FThe case was sent to Bournemouth Crown
OL,19,FCourt for a further hearing on 6 March
OL,20,Fand the defendant was released on
OL,21,Fconditional bail.
