OL,6,FFollowing Zac's death, his father Josh
OL,7,FRoe said in a statement: "Words cannot
OL,8,Fdescribe the pain I'm feeling, my
OL,9,Fheart is broken. You are my little
OL,10,Fangel. I love you more than anything
OL,11,Fin this world, you are my best buddy."
OL,13,FGrandfather Chris Roe added: "Zac,
OL,14,Fthere are just no words to find. I
OL,15,Fjust want to thank you for the
OL,16,Fwonderful and fun-filled memories we
OL,17,Fshared on your short journey of your
OL,18,Flife.
